Port 2222
ListenAddress 0.0.0.0
Protocol 2
HostKey /run/bbm-secrets/repository-ssh/ssh_host_ed25519_key
AuthorizedKeysFile /data/repository-ssh/authorized_keys
PubkeyAuthentication yes
AuthenticationMethods publickey
PasswordAuthentication no
KbdInteractiveAuthentication no
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
PermitEmptyPasswords no
PermitRootLogin no
UsePAM no
AllowUsers borg
PermitTTY no
X11Forwarding no
AllowTcpForwarding no
AllowAgentForwarding no
PermitTunnel no
PermitUserRC no
GatewayPorts no
StrictModes yes
LoginGraceTime 30
ClientAliveInterval 10
ClientAliveCountMax 30
MaxAuthTries 3
MaxSessions 10
MaxStartups 10:30:60
LogLevel VERBOSE
